以下是完整可用的HTML代码：

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A股市场日报 - 2025年7月14日</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 0;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 30px 40px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0 0 6px 0;
            color: #0f172a;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        h1 small {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .subhead {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .subhead .date {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .badge-green {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 28px 0 12px 0;
            padding-left: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 8px 0 16px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        th {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
        }
        td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .up { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
        .down { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
        .data-table th:first-child, .data-table td:first-child { width: 28%; }
        .section-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 12px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container { padding: 20px 16px; }
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
